 />\n<br />\n對sales黎講, 有錢賺話知個客黎自南非咩"},{"pid":"87dcf64ed75fba6989b28620d5216b7e6e4c8f91","tid":109055,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多支那狗來港買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基金又好, 股票又好, 保險又好, 倫敦金都好啦<br />\n<br />\n對sales黎講, 有錢賺話知個客黎自南非咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個客黎自半人馬座都無問題架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}